        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "高原反应的处方预防药——出发前至少提前一周咨询医生"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "高原反應的處方預防藥——出發前至少提前一週諮詢醫生"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Their bag to carry builds independence — and means you're not carrying absolutely everything" : {
